data.description:
Welcome Home! Go and show this very charming 1,905 Sqft home with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Located on a quiet culdesac with a spacious deck and backyard area that is just under half an acre. Upstairs family room could easily be used as a fourth bedroom with the addition of a door. You won't regret viewing this well-maintained, mostly renovated home! With gorgeous new floors and sub flooring throughout. The kitchen hosts butcher block countertops and top of the line appliances. The well-established Summerhill subdivision is close to I-77 and I-20, minutes from Sand Hill and Fort Jackson.
 HOA is optional.
